sequenceDiagram
  participant M as Model
  participant P as Provider Runtime
  participant C as Core Runtime
  participant T as Tool Runtime
  participant S as Session Log

  M->>P: text delta
  P->>C: ModelEvent.text_delta
  C->>S: append text_delta
  M->>P: tool-call delta args part 1
  P->>P: assemble partial args
  M->>P: tool-call delta args part 2
  P->>P: parse complete input
  P->>C: ModelEvent.tool_intent
  C->>S: append tool_intent.proposed
  C->>T: validate / permission / execute
  T->>C: Observation
  C->>S: append observation
